# Cortex Command, with Flydigi Apex 2 in mind
JoyXY wasd deadzone 40 # Move
CamXY mouse 100 # Move Cursor

# Triggers
TriggerR M1 # Fire
TriggerL M2 # ?
BumperL Q # Prev Body
BumperR E # Next Body

# Face buttons
ActionV Space
ActionH R # Reload
ActionA W # Up / Jump
ActionB S # Down / Crouch

# Menu Buttons
MenuL Tab
MenuR Escape # Exit
